<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='918841' id='t-918841'>Dalia Mogahed: I would say,
don't let this stage distract you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='921787' id='t-921787'>I'm completely ordinary.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='923821' id='t-923821'>I'm not an exception.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='925447' id='t-925447'>My story is not unusual.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='927491' id='t-927491'>I am as ordinary as they come.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='930498' id='t-930498'>When you look at Muslims
